Description: Allow to run 'Cppcheck' (https://cppcheck.sourceforge.io/) on C/C++ files with a R command or a 'RStudio' addin. The report appears in the RStudio viewer pane as a formatted HTML file. It is also possible to get this report with a 'Shiny' application.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: htmlwidgets, rstudioapi, xml2, utils, shiny, V8, rmarkdown
Suggests: shinyFiles, shinyAce, shinybusy, shinyWidgets, shinyjqui, htmltools
SystemRequirements: cppcheck
URL: https://github.com/stla/cppcheckR
